This paper deals with the privacy and traceability of a cryptocurrency, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves data analysis and machine learning techniques, which could be categorized under cybernetics (cs.CY) and databases (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper uses statistical methods to estimate the effectiveness of heuristics, which could be classified under machine learning (cs.LG) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
